snippet: Perry Jones III had 14 points with 12 rebounds, and fourth-ranked Baylor remained undefeated with a 61-52 victory over visiting Texas A&M in the Big 12 opener for both teams.
abstract: Baylor remains undefeated in men's college basketball with a 61-52 victory over Texas A&M.
lead_paragraph: Perry Jones III had 14 points with 12 rebounds, and fourth-ranked Baylor remained undefeated with a 61-52 victory over visiting Texas A&M in the Big 12 opener for both teams.

headline.seo: Baylor Still Unbeaten After Victory Over Texas A&M
